name: Improvised Seaforium Pacemaker

spells.description:
Equip: Repurpose a Seaforium charge to give your heart a kick, causing your first ability every 60 sec to trigger Explosive Adrenaline, granting 3,169 Critical Strike for 15 sec.

While exploding, Critical Strikes cause you to blow up again, extending this duration by 1 sec, up to 15 times.

description: It's just crazy enough to work...

spells.description:
Use: Channel to vent flames for 2 sec, dealing 2.5 million Fire damage split between all nearby enemies.

Mechanical enemies become Superheated, taking 119,718  additional Fire damage when struck by your next harmful ability. (2 Min Cooldown)
Equip: Don the mantle of the Trashmaster.
Equip: Damaging a target has a low chance to call upon the power of the Blessed Weapon Grip, granting you 10 stacks that increase your highest secondary stat by 185. These stacks fade over 30 sec.
